    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve honestly gotta see this absolute beauty in person. I\u2019ve babied this car since the day I got it, and it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in truly pristine condition\u2014not a single scratch, dent, or smudge anywhere. It drives like a total dream and has been kept tucked away in a garage. I\u2019m genuinely sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to have a blast with it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 44500.0,
