    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Available now is a peerless 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, a definitive example of JDM engineering excellence. This specimen retains its factory-original 2JZ-GTE power plant, featuring a sequential twin-turbocharger configuration with zero shaft play and optimal boost pressure. Power is delivered through the legendary Getrag V160 six-speed manual gearbox to a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring visceral mechanical engagement. The chassis integrity is absolute, featuring untouched double-wishbone suspension and original forged alloy wheels. Documented compression testing confirms perfect uniformity across all six cylinders. With a flawless undercarriage, original VIN tags on every panel, and a pristine interior, this is a museum-grade investment for the serious enthusiast.",
